content: I'm new to FHIR. Is there a way to generate FHIR object model from custom profile for a Java project using a Tool or should be manual ? Thank you.

Hi @Ranjith I know that @Claude Nanjo has been working on a code generator for custom profiles (for different programming languages incl. Java and C#). But I don't know the current state of the project. Claude may be able to help you out.
Thanks a lot...Michel. I will check with Claude for information
No problem. FYI we are planning to integrate code generation into our http://simplifier.net environment, but this is still on our roadmap.
Looked at the information briefly...very nice.. it would greatly help with my development for understanding FHIR modules. Thanks
